FIXES APPLIED:
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

FIX 1: TREND DIRECTION FILTER
- Detects trend using ADX + EMA20/EMA50
- BLOCKS LONG in STRONG_DOWNTREND
- BLOCKS SHORT in STRONG_UPTREND
- Only trades WITH the trend!

FIX 2: ADX MOMENTUM FILTER
- When ADX > 50, momentum is EXTREME
- S/R levels typically get BROKEN
- SKIP all trades when ADX > 50

FIX 3: ALL 3 CONFIRMATIONS REQUIRED
- OLD: 2/3 confirmations (too lenient!)
- NEW: ALL 3 required (candlestick + volume + RSI)
- Higher quality entries only

FIX 4: TIGHTER STOP-LOSS
- OLD: MIN_PRICE_MOVE_PERCENT = 2% (= $20 loss!)
- NEW: MIN_PRICE_MOVE_PERCENT = 0.8% (= $8 max loss)
- Exchange-level stop-loss now limits to ~$6-8

